{"tid":353880,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"旅發局招標風波電競節韓星疑由林建岳公司代理","createTime":"2017-08-10T03:41:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-10T20:33:03.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ac5e576640d713acfc6b67f9938a28040262c4ac","tid":353880,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T03:41:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20116937&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170810\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20116937%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170810&d=cms4Z2pWDrUixDO0cdo5%2FNtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=03a727e3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20116937%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170810&h=051c2901\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20116937&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170810</a><br />\n<br />\n旅發局招標風波<br />\n電競節韓星疑由林建岳公司代理<br />\n<br />\n港聞&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】由政府撥3,500萬元籌備的電競音樂節活動風波尚未停止，香港電子競技創辦人鍾培生昨於《明報》刊頭版全版聲明，質疑電競節表演韓國藝人由旅發局主席林建岳（圖）旗下寰亞代理。記者曾向林建岳查詢，林透過律師行發聲明否認。<br />\n雖然旅發局早前澄清指，中標公司非林旗下子公司，亦不涉任何既得利益，但本報發現，林建岳與中標的168 Production（下稱168）關係非淺，更是韓國SM娛樂在港的主要合作夥伴。<br />\n由林建岳持有77.78%股權的寰亞，是SM娛樂在港的長期合作夥伴，SM旗下藝人在港舉辦的演唱會大多數是由寰亞或SM子公司Dream maker主辦。據寰亞傳媒2014年9月發佈公告中，當時寰亞宣佈與SM簽訂有約束力的藝人代理合作備忘錄，將出任3位SM的藝人及音樂團體於中國的獨家代理人，包括張力尹、F（x）及EXO。資料顯示，寰亞亦是韓團Super Junior的香港代理人。<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n林發律師信否認事件<br />\n<br />\n是次來港參與「SMTOWN SPECIAL STAGE in HONG KONG」（SMTOWN）演唱會正正包括Super Junior的東海、銀赫及藝聲、F（x）Luna及男團EXO。林建岳透過律師行發聲明指，SMTOWN的表演者 （即F（x）及EXO）並非寰亞傳媒所代理，但未有回應與SM的合作備忘錄是否仍有效以及雙方的關係。<br />\n中標的168本身只有舉辦演唱會經驗，未見有舉辦大型活動的經驗。本報翻查資料發現，168網站有一間名為興明亞洲工程有限公司的友情連結，兩間公司同用九龍灣國際展貿中心的單位作登記，本報查冊發現，168唯一董事為陳詠詩，而興明的創辦人為陳木興。本報致電陳詠詩，她指與陳木興是父女，但拒回答電競節當中演唱會項目外判予哪間公司。旅發局回覆指，168中標後將電競項目外判予電競公司CGA，SMTOWN演唱會由168提供。<br />\n■記者梁偉聰<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n「工廈大王」孫　富三代鍾培生爆料<br />\n<br />\n港聞&nbsp;6小時前"},{"pid":"69b5bda01840c82a81fa42e92191fbba2b553b43","tid":353880,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T03:42:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20170810/large/a0704a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170810%2Flarge%2Fa0704a.gif&h=f5aea5e2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d9e08a92d8504245bf415658854416ea8cc29276","tid":353880,"uid":118434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T04:28:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d92737b2ed4181c2b89b302962bcd5ce436ae491","tid":353880,"uid":80814,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T04:50:37.000Z","msg":"其實都好明顯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <br />\n我之前一路以為個SM TOWN係寰亞主辦,<br />\n<br />\n到我朋友畀林鄭、林建岳同SM藝人合照我睇, <br />\n<br />\n先知係旅發局搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39a556b5064b800304c8a9ce132303369af55674","tid":353880,"uid":39800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T05:33:33.000Z","msg":"屌那星<br />\n官商勾結<br />\n黑箱作業"},{"pid":"a81f1d1d620cde8790c5043113082828968ca45e","tid":353880,"uid":5523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T05:37:17.000Z","msg":"sm娛樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a59fc8b4cb9843ff76bdb8ab6f422e88bdc8d1c","tid":353880,"uid":52590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T07:18:22.000Z","msg":"三千幾萬都搞到成pat屎咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a07c013412fbf93807f021